snippet.title: Neo Cab - Release Date Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Neo Cab will release on Nintendo Switch on October 3! Play the demo today and pre-order the game to continue your journey.

Learn more about Neo Cab! https://bit.ly/2kCJP08

#NintendoSwitch #NeoCab
